title.jp: Kouhai to Tonari wa Nani wo Morai Mizu

synopsis: Introducing the Usakame High School tennis club! To prepare for the national tournament, the girls practice their super killer moves.

title.jp: Kouhai to Soko no Ke Soko no Ke Oba ga Tooru

synopsis: Nishi and Ayako run into each other as they arrive at school. Ayako's musings about Nishi's scooter are interrupted when they run into another member of the tennis club doing something rather strange on the stairs.

title.jp: Kouhai to Hyorori to Neko no Kageboushi

synopsis: Ayako desperately attempts to befriend a stray cat, but the cat seems determined to hate her. Meanwhile, the other club members seem to have no trouble making friends with the cat and even a strange man named Sekiguchi-san.

title.jp: Kouhai to Fuyou Shitataru Oto Sunari

synopsis: Shibakusa-sensei, the tennis club advisor, shows up to school hungover. She reluctantly agrees to attend practice when the team begs her to come.

title.jp: Kouhai to Harukaze Natte Shiraha no Ya

synopsis: A group of familiar faces arrive at Usakame High for a practice match. Can the Usakame tennis club beat their old rivals?

title.jp: Kouhai to Nobe Nitsure Tatsu Hinaga Kana

synopsis: The girls decide to go to Kurumi's house after their practice match to discuss the game. When they enter the door, they're greeted by Kurumi's panicked father who screams that there's an emergency in progress!

title.jp: Kouhai to Itsuka Dete Aru Hiru no Tsuki

synopsis: Kinako suddenly wakes up in the middle of class. Has everything that's happened until now been a dream? And who are Bamyan and Tasuku?

title.jp: Kouhai to Mizu ga Torori to Haru no Kaze
Kouhai to Oku Shounin to Tsuredachite

synopsis: Kinako is stuck running the family candy shop for the day. As her friends from school come to visit one after another, she attempts to keep herself entertained, sometimes at their expense.

title.jp: Kouhai to Ake Yuku Haru no Arashi ka na

synopsis: Ayako and Kinako are busy with their respective committee meetings, leaving Nishi and Kurumi to hang out and practice alone together.

title.jp: Kouhai to Waga Na Yobaren Hashigure

synopsis: With their final tournament as a team approaching, it's time to get serious. Who will be chosen to play doubles with Ayako?

title.jp: Kouhai to Ki Naru Tefutefu Hitotsu Mishi

synopsis: With their own graduation approaching, Kurumi and Ayako think back to when their seniors graduated from the tennis club. Will their memories send them spiraling into depression or inspire them to play better at the upcoming tournament?
